{"tid":448200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲各位巴絲一招收哂Unicef街站班人皮","createTime":"2017-10-26T04:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T04:17:48.000Z","uid":83776,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d16d57ef1a23bdf74b247404431136f3f824519f","tid":448200,"uid":83776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"佢老母 一行過黎sell我:<br />\n先生 好多兒童等緊你幫架<br />\n每日捐5蚊 就幫到好多人架喇<br />\n<br />\n然後我唔岀聲 望一望佢:<br />\n不如你答我你地每個月攞左我地幾多錢做人工呀？<br />\n佢即刻收左聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n扮撚哂有愛心其實係假撚<br />\n為左賺錢乜都做得岀<br />\n呼籲各位ching唔好中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要捐就自己直接過數/網上捐款都得<br />\n唔好比啲假撚利用人地同情心賺錢！"},{"pid":"01700506bd3d9ae851202bd18114075a0b130174","tid":448200,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"我啤一啤佢，直行算"},{"pid":"ebe05d5230542e23f8550b73a218bc4aafc53078","tid":448200,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"163a5f29b878f9d9249ba55cc66ed876227874f1","tid":448200,"uid":83776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啤一啤佢，直行算</blockquote><br />\n忍左好耐 日日去到邊都見到呢堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708bbe438277d8a793ff0e12e0dfbe2f11788535","tid":448200,"uid":83776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦 人地都係打份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲野唔可以算<br />\n要令更多人提高警覺"},{"pid":"6cbb80d5bd2e18f9f935ac0a1edf0e69a8fdfa9e","tid":448200,"uid":12536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:17:48.000Z","msg":"咪撚開街站 咪慳返啲錢捐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前睇過有資料show返出黎 啲捐款for行政費佔6成 跟住真正捐得3成左右"}]}